source: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_050<tab>At last... The power to reclaim what is mine. What is <var 1A 02 /var>ours<var 1A 01 /var>...
target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_050<tab>Le nimbe royal... Je vais enfin pouvoir rompre le sceau de l'épée et libérer son vrai pouvoir...

source:
TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_051The will of Queen Gunnhildr shall not be denied.
All who oppose Bozja must fall.
target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_051<tab>Moi et la lame sacrée de Bozja accomplirons la dernière volonté de Gunnhildr... et exterminerons tous ceux qui ont bafoué notre nom...

source: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MIKOTO_000_052<tab>By the gods... She has become a vessel for the blade's power!
target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MIKOTO_000_052<tab>Garde-la-Reine, sous sa véritable forme<var 1D /var>! Nous arrivons trop tard<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_100No... No, we have suffered too long for it to end this way.
Bozja is ours! If we cannot have it, no one will!
target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_100<tab>Non<var 1D /var>! Je porte en moi l'amertume de tout un peuple... Bozja mérite de subir notre furie<var 1D /var>!!!
